{"tid":1623882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請謹記  我們不是缺乏政治智慧的林奠","createTime":"2019-10-05T02:07:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T02:36:40.000Z","uid":70524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"37208f757e36653e3d0f8b6751e5fd9010de589e","tid":1623882,"uid":70524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:07:46.000Z","msg":"運動至今  我們依舊沒有大台<br />\n<br />\n沒有人可以代表我 同時 我亦不能代表你<br />\n<br />\n所有行動是靠著集體分析 討論去實踐<br />\n<br />\n不是所有post也是風向post <br />\n<br />\n不是所有人也是風向撚<br />\n<br />\n我寧可你認為所有人也是兄弟<br />\n<br />\n所有意見也是真誠<br />\n<br />\n也不願你們一意孤行 在危難中覺得只有自己是對的<br />\n<br />\n一直讓運動進行下去 依賴的是集體智慧  <br />\n<br />\n非獨裁權力  非大台宣言<br />\n<br />\n我們與怪獸博鬥時 別讓自己也成了怪獸<br />\n<br />\n知易行難 希望大家靜下來 想一想<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>天佑我城</strong></span>"},{"pid":"e8761259631cbef77354e2a9581cfd6297678063","tid":1623882,"uid":70524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:11:40.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"9d47771943648bde89db84eef101714d79da73fa","tid":1623882,"uid":70524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:11:50.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"ff9e9be83f2cf239f089edf7eca28f056c684172","tid":1623882,"uid":70524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:12:00.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"1754c71b59d6e34954131304f4bc0a8f9e2b2d36","tid":1623882,"uid":70524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:12:53.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"533222181c02706b0f615182c4397f76f0efb8d3","tid":1623882,"uid":70524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:13:04.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"9d1603e53251e9b4140c0d12c804195901a31a44","tid":1623882,"uid":70524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:13:14.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"ee4cfc9658e851da1ec971d913b9fa298d408426","tid":1623882,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT